cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.GT 

This paper deals with computer vision and deep learning techniques to generate complete images of occluded people. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses GANs and U-nets, which are popular deep learning architectures used in image processing, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also discusses the optimization of a loss function, which is a common technique in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category. The paper also deals with generating 3D data, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and the use of data from a video game could fall under cs.GT (Computer Graphics).
